      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. While the engine currently starts, it suffers from significant oil leaks and a persistent knocking sound that will require professional attention. The body shows extensive rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears. This car is best suited as a donor for parts or for a buyer prepared for a complete mechanical and cosmetic overhaul.",
