    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You've found it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I've babied it since day one, and it truly shows. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself why it's such a gem!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
