      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned Double VANOS system. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced with VAC-coated components to ensure long-term durability. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip M-Variable Lock differential. The chassis remains factory-firm with no bushing deflection, and the engine maintains a crisp 8,000 RPM redline with perfect compression across all cylinders. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation, this specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
